  "desc": "Experience elevated uptown living at one of Hoboken's most sought-after luxury residences within the Hudson Tea community. This beautifully appointed, fully furnished one-bedroom plus den, two-full-bath home offers a seamless blend of style, comfort, and convenience. The open-concept layout features expansive living and dining spaces, oversized windows, high ceilings, and wide-plank hardwood floors. The modern chef's kitchen is outfitted with quartz countertops, premium stainless steel appliances, and sleek European-style cabinetry, creating the perfect setting for both everyday living and entertaining. Thoughtfully upgraded throughout, this turnkey residence showcases custom closets that maximize storage and organization, designer window treatments, and sophisticated wallpaper accents that add texture to the space. The generously sized primary suite features a walk in closet and an en-suite bath with double vanity. A versatile den with two large closets provides the flexibility for a home office, nursery, guest room, or additional living area, while the second full bathroom offers added convenience for visitors and everyday living. Residents enjoy access to an exceptional collection of amenities, including a 24-hour concierge, fitness center, landscaped rooftop terraces with grilling areas and fire pits, children's playroom, shuttle service to the PATH, and access to additional Hudson Tea community amenities, including a rooftop pool. Perfectly situated in Hoboken's desirable north end, this premier address places you moments from the waterfront promenade, boutique shopping, acclaimed dining, parks, and convenient transportation options to Manhattan. Offered fully furnished and enhanced with thoughtfully curated upgrades, this move-in-ready home delivers effortless luxury in one of Hoboken's most coveted waterfront communities. Covered parking available next door for rent!",
